SUMMARY:Bryan City Council special meeting (HELD)
LOCATION:City of Bryan
DESCRIPTION:HELD 6/26: approved a replacement RELLIS data-center tax abatement (~$298M / 5 jobs; 10-yr min PILOT ~$14.9M); unanimous among 4 of 7 present; new owner has a September construction deadline. Tracker BV-0059. Confidence: Reported.
