DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260707T120000
SUMMARY:Brazos County Commissioners Court regular meeting (HELD)
LOCATION:Brazos County Administration Building, 200 S. Texas Ave., Bryan
DESCRIPTION:HELD 7/7: posted agenda included a $1M GME wire transfer, Public Defender Oversight Board nominations, a Whitley Penn audit engagement, an Old Reliance Rd Phase II change order ($239,747.41), FY27 vehicle purchases, interim comp-guideline additions, MUD No. 7 (Live Oaks Ranch) development agreement, and a $1,825,000 real-property purchase; outcomes pending minutes. Tracker BV-0091. Confidence: Official (agenda).
END:VEVENT
