UID:bvbrief-20260709-cscouncil@brazosvalley
DTSTAMP:20260712T220000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260709
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260710
SUMMARY:College Station City Council regular meeting (HELD)
DESCRIPTION:HELD 7/9: consent agenda approved unanimously (~$1.22M, 6 items); after public hearings, unanimously changed land use (7.2 ac) and zoning (8 ac) on Harvey Mitchell Pkwy S to enable multi-family housing; approved 4-3 a Wolf Pen Creek UDO vehicle-sales amendment (Smith, Wright, Shafer opposed). Tracker BV-0083..BV-0085. Confidence: Official (city record).
END:VEVENT
