DESCRIPTION:HELD 6/30: 80+ attendees; GM Alan Day said the region will not run out of water; district manages 8 aquifers, monitors 224 wells; questions on data-center/SpaceX Terafab water use. Informational, no vote. Tracker BV-0073. Confidence: Reported.
